Beautiful Halong Bay
Apr 2023 â€¢ Friends
We did this visit as part of our holiday with Mercury Holidays - Impressions of Vietnam.

Excellent trip. Rooms were lovely, bathroom ideal. Food was excellent. Views brilliant. Would definitely recommend it.
We visited the Luon caves in a bamboo boat and also went to a beach for a swim. Did Tai Chi and engaged in a cooking demonstration
Staff very helpful. Drinks available - card or cash.
Beautiful area. Very calming atmosphere and beautiful views.
Quite alot of rubbish but I believe the Government are looking at getting the Boat Owners involved in clearing it up.
