A night in Ha Long Bay
Nov 2022 â€¢ Friends
Magnificent views. And Nature in all glory. The beautiful cruise surrounded by nature. Then go on a boat to sung sot caves , followed by climbing to the caves ( only for the strong hearted ). Then lo and behold the wonderful sights in the cave. Then a small boat ride to Tito beach. Fun and frolic there. Boat ride back to the main boat. Then Sunset watch if you are lucky !.
A night of peace and tranquility in the anchored Big Boat, surrounded by the hills. A beautiful sunrise reflected in the seas.
Then a small boat ride . And an opportunity for the daring to go kayaking . And for others go through the surprise cave and surrounded by hills all round . And then Monkey watch and the antics of the smart ones.
Well all good things have to end : Ride back in the Small boat ,to the mother boat and then cruise back to the pier.
Unmissable !
Written November 17, 2022
